<title>USA: Seibels Bruce Group registers offering.</title>
<headline>Seibels Bruce Group registers offering.</headline>
<dateline>COLUMBIA, S.C. 1997-03-27</dateline>
<text>
<p>Seibels Bruce Group Inc said it has filed a registration statement with the Securities and Exchange Commission to register a total of about 1.4 million shares of common stock.</p>
<p>About 7.4 million shares will be offered by a shareholder of the company, and four million shares will be offered by the company.</p>
<p>These share numbers do not reflect a 1-for-4 reverse stock split which will be submitted for shareholder approval next month at the company's annual shareholder meeting.</p>
